<h2>Head of Marketing</h2>
<p>gitti is a direct-to-consumer beauty start-up based in Berlin. We are now entering the next exciting phase of rapid growth and are looking for a <strong>Head of Marketing</strong> (m/w/d) who gets excited about building ground-breaking marketing campaigns that live across social and digital platforms and influencer marketing. Reporting to our Managing Director, you will lead the Marketing team and develop digital campaigns that drive sales, brand awareness and disrupt the beauty market.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Your tasks</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Responsible for further building gitti’s brand with a clear marketing strategy throughout all digital channels</li>
<li>Define, manage and execute our social media strategy including customer reach, engagement rate and influencer collaborations and programs for new customer acquisition channels</li>
<li>Mange and ensure new customer growth targets</li>
<li>Define and execute CRM strategy to further grow the retention rate</li>
<li>Constantly test new acquisition channels and show ROI potential</li>
<li>Build up weekly and monthly marketing reports to track budgets, new customer growth, profitability and all relevant KPIs</li>
<li>Manage marketing budget efficiently in order to help gitti achieve our short- and long-term growth objectives and profitability targets according to our business plan</li>
<li>Manage your direct reports with structure, guidance and mentorship</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Your skills</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bachelor’s and/or Master’s degree in marketing, business or related field</li>
<li>+3 years of experience in online marketing channels such as social media marketing, influencer marketing, paid social advertising and search engine marketing</li>
<li>Have the ability to balance an outstanding analytical, metrics-focused thinking with the strong creative mind needed to develop breakthrough campaigns</li>
<li>You have a deep understanding of KPIs and have a data-driven mindset, you must be the voice that says: “let’s look at the data...”</li>
<li>Have a passion for hands on testing: bias to action, think out of the box, tracking results</li>
<li>You have previously led a team and have solid experience developing and coaching people</li>
<li>Ideally you have experience in a growing DTC/online brand with a community of engaged users &amp; have a hands-on experience in creating digital and has participated in building and scaling a differentiated online brand</li>
<li>Fluent in both english &amp; german: written &amp; verbal</li>
<li>Must be excited in creating a disruptive brand in beauty</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Your benefits</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>360° ownership of all marketing activities of a fast-growing multi-country direct-to-consumer beauty brand</li>
<li>Face exciting challenges in a fast-paced start-up environment and receive regular feedback and coaching to exceed your goals</li>
<li>Experience the power of teamwork and fun in a highly motivated, international and empowering team</li>
<li>Attractive salary package</li>
<li>Get the chance to revolutionize the beauty industry</li>
<li>Central location in Berlin</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Sounds good? </strong></p>
<p>Then let's do that and send us your application to <span><a href="mailto:people@gitti.de">people@gitti.de</a></span>. Please don't forget to state your salary expectations and a possible starting date. We're looking forward to hearing from you!</p>
